{"tid":819693,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"百里香食評","createTime":"2018-09-15T04:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T16:18:25.000Z","uid":34777,"like":67,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a83b5a825f67088ac7d9f6871b29e87c11fef0c8","tid":819693,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"受到打手慘過番印度啟發<br />\n決定千里迢迢由大西北去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講咁多 即刻去圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由個餐湯講起先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/114649_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F114649_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=bb7268d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲湯幾夠味 都算幾好飲<br />\n最重要係新鮮夠熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蒜蓉包唔熱是唔好食的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到主菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梗係食燒春雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/120053_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F120053_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=f399330e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻雞真係非常有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好夠熱同juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一咬落口啲汁啲標哂出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好夠味 唔洗點落bbq醬都夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個脆薯皇好食過M記唔知幾多條街<br />\n又熱又夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋炸得好好 仲keep到啲薯仔味<br />\n食完係可以飽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為專程帶埋老母嚟<br />\n所以叫多個餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揀咗米蘭式煙肉芝士茄茸焗豬柳配飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/120750_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F120750_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=1d7a1153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲豬柳好嫩 又夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲芝士多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正過鳩假期啲乜邪惡隱世芝士拉絲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （呢間啲芝士都可以拉絲的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n惟獨個飯可以乾身啲就仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個價咁都收貨了<br />\n<br />\n最後壓軸登場係平時冇嘅甜品 焦糖燉蛋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/121051_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F121051_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=c90d14df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係覺得好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊焦糖厚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又幾夠蛋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為最後1230am前埋單<br />\n每個餐又減5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢間都唔是完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （唔是印度打手巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n佢啲冷氣可以大啲同埋音樂細聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但總括而言 都係一間唔錯又好抵食嘅餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係連老母都話正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4715b29ae5b06eb9a8180970fd9ebde7a4695787","tid":819693,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"第一次打食評<br />\n多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53095868490ba4c7b72308eb02e5408014999f3a","tid":819693,"uid":33359,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcf971d572b44f2b53d06d02547a429db725268","tid":819693,"uid":34777,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"53095868490ba4c7b72308eb02e5408014999f3a","tid":819693,"uid":33359,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"嗰個係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ca7420fa05c8dbf8d7599aacaa7c4b136984dd","tid":819693,"uid":194666,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"你地兩個可以結婚然後日日去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b44b70d733ee4dfbef026cc17dfbac9d58f3ddb","tid":819693,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dcf971d572b44f2b53d06d02547a429db725268","tid":819693,"uid":34777,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"53095868490ba4c7b72308eb02e5408014999f3a","tid":819693,"uid":33359,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"嗰個係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"中立非打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3721ce80e7eba80f4ad3df80bec9b8755490ad","tid":819693,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ca7420fa05c8dbf8d7599aacaa7c4b136984dd","tid":819693,"uid":194666,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"你地兩個可以